---
/**
 * Testimonials Section - Social Proof
 */
---

<section class="py-32 lg:py-48 relative">
  <div class="container-rebellion">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-off-white mb-6">
        Historias de <span class="text-gradient-rebellion">transformación</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-soft-gray">
        Profesionales reales que decidieron tomar el control de su vida
        financiera.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="glassmorphism rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1 mb-4">
          {
            [1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(() => (
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-honey-beehive"
                fill="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              >
                <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
              </svg>
            ))
          }
        </div>
        <p class="text-off-white mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          "Money Training cambió completamente mi perspectiva. Pasé de vivir con
          ansiedad financiera a tener un sistema claro que me da tranquilidad."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-rebellion-green to-rebellion-cyan flex items-center justify-center text-glimpse-space font-bold"
          >
            MC
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-off-white font-semibold">María C.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-soft-gray">Emprendedora Digital</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="glassmorphism rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1 mb-4">
          {
            [1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(() => (
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-honey-beehive"
                fill="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              >
                <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
              </svg>
            ))
          }
        </div>
        <p class="text-off-white mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          "Lo que más valoro es que Claudia enseña desde la experiencia real. No
          son teorías, son estrategias que funcionan en la vida real."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-honey-beehive to-orange-400 flex items-center justify-center text-glimpse-space font-bold"
          >
            JR
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-off-white font-semibold">Jorge R.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-soft-gray">Consultor Independiente</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="glassmorphism rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1 mb-4">
          {
            [1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(() => (
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-honey-beehive"
                fill="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              >
                <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
              </svg>
            ))
          }
        </div>
        <p class="text-off-white mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          "Duplicé mis ingresos en 8 meses aplicando lo que aprendí. La
          comunidad y el soporte son increíbles."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold"
          >
            LP
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-off-white font-semibold">Laura P.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-soft-gray">Coach de Negocios</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
